scratch/
docs/
deprecated/
steps/
data/generators/
data/generated/

# ── Markdown docs ─────────────────────────────────────────
README.md
README_DEPLOY.md
STADIUM_SYSTEM_GUIDE.md
code_audit_report.md
hackathon_standards_guide.md
plan.md

